<i>adverb</i>: 새삼스레 [새삼스레], 새삼 [새삼] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>새삼스레 [새삼스레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. anew; afresh</dd><br>
<dd>이미 느끼거나 알고 있었지만 다시 새롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>Newly again, although one had already felt or knew.</dd><br>
<dd>2. suddenly; unexpectedly</dd><br>
<dd>전에 안 하던 일을 하여 갑작스러운 느낌이 들게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sudden manner, by doing something one had not done before.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>새삼 [새삼]</dt><br>
<dd>1. anew; afresh</dd><br>
<dd>이미 느끼거나 알고 있었지만 다시 새롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>Newly again, although one had already felt that way or knows.</dd><br>
<dd>2. suddenly; unexpectedly</dd><br>
<dd>전에 안 하던 일을 하여 갑작스러운 느낌이 들게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sudden manner, by doing something one had not done before.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>